2 - Old: I only want meat. Tilt the spoon slightly when feeding me. Feed me with larger bites
17 - Old: I only want vegetables. Feed me in small bites..

9 - Old: Avoid the vegetables and give me only rice and chicken. Keep the bites small and tilt the spoon slightly.

0 - Old: Feed me all the rice first, then alternate between chicken and vegetables
1 - Old: I want alternate bites of chicken and rice. I prefer to be fed larger bites and for the spoon to be further away from me.
3 - Old: Start with the vegetables, then the meat. Keep the bites small.
4 - Old: Alternate between rice and vegetables, but do not feed me chicken. Keep the spoon far from my mouth.
5 - Old: Feed me all the chicken first, then the rice. Use smaller bites and be careful not to tilt the spoon too much.
6 - Old: I prefer alternate bites of rice, chicken and vegetables. Do not repeat any bites. Feed me evenly without tilting the spoon.
7 - Old: Give me two bites of meat first, then alternate between vegetables and rice. Make sure to tilt the spoon a little higher
8 - Old: I want all the vegetables first, followed by alternating bites of chicken and rice. Keep the bites medium-sized and keep the spoon far from me.
10 - Old: Start with the chicken, then the vegetables, and end with the rice. Keep the spoon close to me.
11 - Old: Feed me only the rice, one spoonful at a time. Keep the bites large.
12 - Old: Alternate between rice, chicken, and vegetables. Keep the spoon at a distance and use small bites.
13 - Old: I want one bite of chicken followed by two bites of rice. Feed me with tilted spoonfuls.
14 - Old: Feed me vegetables first, then alternate rice and meat. Use small bites and tilt the spoon slightly. Also keep the spoon close to me.
15 - Old: Give me larger bites of chicken, followed by smaller bites of rice. Feed me with a tilt in the spoon and do not come too close to me.
16 - Old: Feed me rice first, then alternate between chicken and vegetables. Keep the spoon tilted slightly upwards.
18 - Old: Start with a bite of vegetables, then alternate between chicken and rice.
19 - Old: I have no preference in the sequence, but I prefer the spoon to be closer to me.
